-- Migration 152: move 'Exam Voucher' section from short_description
-- into additional_note for every CompTIA course that carries it.
--
-- Generated by scripts/local-dev/generate-comptia-exam-voucher-migration.php
-- (scrapes tertiarycourses.com.sg as the source of truth).
--
-- Idempotency:
--   additional_note: UPDATE guarded by NOT LIKE '%Exam Voucher%' so a
--     re-run on an already-merged value is a no-op. If no admin-scope
--     row exists, INSERT one.
--   short_description: REPLACE(value, '<scraped voucher block>', '')
--     no-ops on rows where the block has already been stripped.
--
-- Side effect: fixes the well-known 'Autodesk Exam Voucher' copy-paste
-- bug to 'CompTIA Exam Voucher' in the migrated copy.

